You are Gob the miner, and you are trapped in a cave. Use your dynamite and the environment to trap Man Bear Swine and blow him up before he catches up to you and eats you alive.

This Unity game was created in 8 hours for an MSDN-sponsored game development hackathon at the University of South Florida, on June 27, 2015. It features original artwork by Ike Yousuf, bomberman-style explosions, and randomly generated maze levels.

